Code Source: Lab Codes
Code Modifications: https://www.w3schools.com

Different Viewport:
I used 1200px for Laptops, 1000px for Tablets and 786px for Mobile as there are the common
resolutions for such devices.

I used a linear-gradient to right for the home page and a linear-gradient to bottom right on the contact me page.

I used a simple white to dark grey color scheme for a simple sleep view of the page.